content: It is very easy to use and learn. The design is clean and pleasing. But my question is how to work the music player with spotify? Thanks
replyContent: Thanks! The player should work fine with Spotify without any problem, but try to go to the KWGT settings, then preferred music player, and then set it to "automatic".

So I'm giving this 5 stars because I think it's incredible, however I'm confused by the fact that when I use a music widget here, it doesn't show the artwork it just has like a blank placeholder image, what's the best way to fix this?
replyContent: Hello, maybe you need to turn on the option "show album art in the lockscreen" on your music player app's settings
